
Prerequisites: you must have openvswitch running, or a physical OpenFlow switch.
The configuration is made in file of_config.py.

To run the tests with Twister Framework, you must:
- generate the tests,
- copy of_config.py, all Python files from oflib folder and oflib/oflib.zip into twister/lib, on Central Engine.

To generate the tests, you must run:
- python tools/basic_parser.py
- python tools/caps_parser.py
- python tools/errormsg_parser.py
- python tools/pktact_parser.py

"oftest_parser" is the library used for generating all the tests.

The tests are created in "tests" folder.
